snippet.title: Quote Codes - iOS Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Quote Codes launches on January 18, 2018 on the App Store. Pre-order the game here – https://goo.gl/XMPwBr

Quote Codes is a word puzzle game where you unlock your favorite quotes by substituting one letter at a time. In every game, each symbol stands for a letter. Your aim is to guess and decode the quotes!

The game will be completely FREE to download and play. 

Decode your favorite quotes and stay inspired all day!

-------------

Visit The Website:
http://www.quotecodes.com
